Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的村子與外面的世界隔絕\N過著自給自足的生活已經有400多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂夏至祭 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了迎接會在每個夏天歸來的祖先的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并祈求他們保佑豐收的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典將開始于明天黎明 一直持續到晚上再結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你們能留下參加完祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 那個玫瑰花窗和尖塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像古畫中的中世紀教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這邊的墻也很古老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這口井也歲數不小了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近的山中住著野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這個村子裏住的是人而不是狼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼胡話 我們是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我族本身和外界的人類不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡 簡直和柯蒂麗亞一摸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那時我還是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是記得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷曼妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這個宅邸 對于這個村莊來說都是不可抹滅的災難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷曼妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件發生在狄奧多村長的書房裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.50,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,560)}夏祭降臨的神諭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜裏的12點女僕在書房……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 當時柯蒂麗亞只有15歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我讓她去更換水壺裏的水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是如此 正好是12點整
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道“正好”12點整？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和其他人看到柯蒂麗亞正用鑰匙進入房中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我看了一下懷表確認了下時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知為何和我在一起的人對時間的證詞完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入書房的柯蒂麗亞立刻尖叫著沖了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們慌忙趕了過去一看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奧多村長被短刀刺中 已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何地上掉落許多金幣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金幣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這個村子裏并不使用金幣這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常都是狄奧多村長集中保管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那夜開始柯蒂麗亞就發高燒臥病不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她退燒後 繼任村長的我就將她逐出了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐出村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時她身上就只有一枚金幣和一只行李箱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她一離開村子 我們就收起了吊橋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個從沒踏出村子半步且不諳世事的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難想象可以她能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人不能留在村裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則會給村裏帶來災難 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個柯蒂麗亞的女兒現在卻在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說散步什麼的 可是我們明明才剛來這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是去散步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是謝爾吉斯的助手 我叫安普羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是好奇為什麼你的皮膚和頭發顏色會與眾不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然知道外面世界不全是金發……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 幫幫我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你呢 有個地方希望你能帶我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對的 可以讓我再摸摸這個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你喜歡 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂麗亞住過的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 就這樣走掉了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人要是被知道帶我們來這裡會出問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是裏面什麼也沒有……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂麗亞小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和還是嬰兒的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是柯蒂麗亞在15歲的時候被趕出這裡的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且他帶走了本來放在這裡的某樣東西 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對的 留下了柯蒂麗亞長大後的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個混沌指向何處？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奧多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前任村長的墳墓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能對墳墓做這麼不敬的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂麗亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫下這個的人是柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親果然是因為子虛烏有的罪名才被趕出村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的罪人在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是維多利加的眸子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我輸給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我錢我倒是可以考慮輸給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 電話怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米 米爾德麗特小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然電話的話 果然這邊有通電嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 村長說他們是過著自給自足的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也覺得很不可思議 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一問那個奇怪的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像他們暗地裏有贊助者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊助者？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 名字是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 叫布萊恩·羅斯可的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩·羅斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是離開村子到外面生活的村民子孫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前這個人就開給村子提供資金了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 牌玩膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我們去看看教堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛剛有狼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西 那個討人厭的老頭子會趕跑它們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 我們那麼走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又纏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾絲啊花邊之類的是在太多了拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩·羅斯可十年前來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他帶著什麼目的來村子的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了給村子通上電不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前 你想想 正是世界大戰剛剛打響的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種時代到深山裏給村子拉上電線有點太倉促了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也正和那張照片被拍下的時間相吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶來了洗澡用的熱水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加入一些冷水後使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 萬一發生什麼事叫我一聲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:10:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}洗…洗…澡 好喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因為暖洋洋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 原來是在唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的維多利加好像又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微喘口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 維多利加 你那邊沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人試圖借此嚇唬我 為了讓我離開這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子給我一種討厭的感覺 太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會保護我的 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 這是紅蕪菁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個彩車 是冬之軍的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這廣場上的男人們會演一出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏之軍和冬之軍戰爭的戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏之軍會打倒冬之軍的大將冬之男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把車子點火燒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們是來侮辱這村子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趕快滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊 居然相信迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個陰暗的村子 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦 要是現在被趕出村子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那個 這家伙到哪都會和人吵架的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這就回房間吧 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙昨天晚上也在圣堂裏鬧事來著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們當著村民的面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把用來裝飾的舊水壺扔進裝著圣水的水缸裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 要做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟醉鬼還會有什麼道理可講啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還嘲笑說那種破爛東西居然還被看得那麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明他們自己見到古董的時候也開心成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 這是祭典的點心 幫你弄來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞蘭先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說了那種話 果然還是挺喜歡這個祭典的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 這個有什麼意義的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個就是安普羅茲先生吧 好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之男 你就化為灰燼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紙人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿水來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞蘭先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他想妨礙祭典被人和紙人換掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾吉斯大人 那是不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘們扔榛果的時候 這個年輕人正巧經過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣場上又聚著很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得要跟紙人調換是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴是愚蠢者的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣終止祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們接下去還有教堂的儀式要舉行 失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都死人了 居然還在繼續祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪啊 這個村裏的村民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 維多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會保護我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌先生 你也是來詢問未來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏之軍勝利了 豐收也得到了保障
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個教堂的話 一直到晚上都不進行日常活動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為教堂連接著那個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來觀看豐收的先祖會經過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 接近這邊的先祖的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會借助于村長之口 來回答孩子們的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌先生 機會難得 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...那個... 我和維多利加...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等一下 安普羅茲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那樣的話 不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那女孩和你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你想問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上 我有個朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今後 可以和維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在數年之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會刮起一股震撼世界的颶風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們的身體都太輕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你們會因為那風而天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的心永遠不會分開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 你也來這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你問了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會不會再長了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高 你這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生什麼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 一聲不吭就突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才都去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書房
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奧多大人就是這樣被人從背後刺中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直刺那個短刀只能看見刀柄那麼深
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奧多大人是個成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而柯蒂麗亞是個15歲的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高的差距太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將短刀插在小孩夠不著的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要深至只能看見刀柄的程度是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那骯臟的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人另有其人 你也是這樣想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧之泉開始訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的碎片 都已被重組了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被重組的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你知道誰是犯人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算知道誰是犯人 我手上也沒有證據
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼出現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算出了人命 就算狼也出現 夏至祭也不可以中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上去 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經聽不見狼的聲音了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我射中一頭了 安普羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第二個人了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.73,0:24:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的罪孽在發出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.10,0:24:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮過去的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.95,0:24:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 有種非常不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
